text: The 1974 Wayne State Tartars football team represented Wayne State University as an independent during the 1974 NCAA Division II football season. In their first year under head coach Dick Lowry, the Tartars compiled a 7–3 record. ==Schedule== ==See also== * 1974 in Michigan ==References== Wayne State Category:Wayne State Warriors football seasons Wayne State Football
